edivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00035.jpg\" alt=\"王哈哈 | 陶泥、面包、食物\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">王哈哈 | 陶泥、面包、食物</figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][sectiondivider]',NULL),(21,1,'2021-02-03 02:28:36','2021-02-03 02:40:07',NULL,'Critique Marathon[tagdivider]Round Three',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'round-three',NULL,'2020-07-04 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary 'Zoom online meeting',_binary '<div class=\"centered\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/4H8GtUFaWT8fwFn9TcjNfg\" target=\"_blank\">活动信息</a></div>[sectiondivider]07.04[sectiontitledivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00036.jpg\" alt=\"王茜瑶 | King Bull\r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">王茜瑶 | King Bull<br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00037.jpg\" alt=\"励明娜 | You’re Not the Only Particle in Universe\r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">励明娜 | You’re Not the Only Particle in Universe<br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][sectiondivider]07.05[sectiontitledivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00038.jpg\" alt=\"黄泽坚 | 工作室\r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">黄泽坚 | 工作室<br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00039.jpg\" alt=\"欧杨 | in/consistent system\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">欧杨 | in/consistent system</figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][sectiondivider]',NULL),(22,1,'2021-02-03 02:44:17','2021-02-03 02:49:26',NULL,'Artist Panel Talk[tagdivider]Simon Denny ⌁ Fang Di',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'simon-denny-fang-di',NULL,'2020-07-25 19:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary 'Zoom online meeting',_binary '<div class=\"centered\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/r4Ore7v7BnZlwj3z-tmkSA\" target=\"_blank\">活动信息</a></div>[sectiondivider]Simon Denny[sectiontitledivider]Simon Denny (1982年出生于新西兰)是一位装置、雕塑和影像艺术家，曾在新西兰奥克兰大学Elam School of Fine Arts及德国法兰克福国立造型艺术学院学习。他在作品思考全球互联网背景下的科技社会现象，以及媒体技术的生产、流通及消费。<br><br>Simon Denny is born in 1982 in Auckland, New Zealand, he studied painting at the Elam School of Fine Arts, University of Auckland before attending the Staatliche Hochschule für Bildende Künste in Frankfurt am Main. His projects explore corporate culture, technology, and the Internet’s effect on society[imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00040.jpg\" alt=\"Simon Denny - Security Through Obscurity, 2020\r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Simon Denny - Security Through Obscurity, 2020<br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00041.jpg\" alt=\"Simon Denny - Current Flow. On the economics of inequality, 2020\r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Simon Denny - Current Flow. On the economics of inequality, 2020<br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00042.jpg\" alt=\"Simon Denny - Power Vest 4, 2019\r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Simon Denny - Power Vest 4, 2019<br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][sectiondivider]Fang Di[sectiontitledivider]方迪是一位艺术家、啾小组的创始人之一、高级工程师、本科毕业于广州美术学院油画系第五工作室，研究生毕业于美国马里兰艺术学院。目前工作于中国深圳和巴布亚新几内亚首都莫尔兹比港。他的作品探讨种族主义于社会阶层。他通过引用社会新闻与时事政治，用多种艺术语言探索城市生活的纠结与意义，寻找特殊群体在全球经济与民族主义的影响下是如何被定义的，成为今天重要的社会裂痕。<br><br>Fang Di is a Chinese artist, founder of Jiu Society, and senior engineer. He&nbsp;graduated from Guangzhou Academy of Fine Arts in 2010 and got an MFA from Maryland Institute College of Art. He is currently based in Shenzhen, China, and Port Moresby, Papua New Guinea. His works delve into racism and social class. By incorporating references to news and politics, his works use multiple vocabularies to investigate our intertwined city life and attempt to pursue the root of special communities how they were defined suffering under the global economy and nationalist, becoming the most important social fracture[imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00043.jpg\" alt=\"Fang Di -部长, 2019\r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Fang Di -部长, 2019<br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00044.jpg\" alt=\"Fang Di - 金饭碗, 2019\r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Fang Di - 金饭碗, 2019<br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00045.png\" alt=\"Fang Di - 現代 HYUNDAI, 2018\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Fang Di - 現代 HYUNDAI, 2018</figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][sectiondivider]',NULL),(23,1,'2021-02-03 03:30:26','2021-02-03 03:36:49',NULL,'Artist Panel Talk[tagdivider]Forensic Architecture ⌁ OMA/AMO',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'forensic-architecture-oma-amo',NULL,'2020-08-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary 'Zoom online meeting',_binary '<div class=\"centered\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/r4Ore7v7BnZlwj3z-tmkSA\" target=\"_blank\">活动信息</a></div>[sectiondivider]Forensic Architecture[sectiontitledivider]Forensic Architecture法证建筑，2010年于伦敦成立的研究机构，总部设在伦敦大学金史密斯学院。他们通过对空间和媒体的深入调研，代表或与受暴力影响的社区、国际检察官、环境正义团体和媒体组织一起调查侵犯人权问题。法证建筑在世界范围内调查政府及商业暴力行为、人权侵犯、环境破坏等问题。他们经常采用开源调查的方式，通过电子或实体模型、3D动画模拟、虚拟现实场景、制图来构建场景，并在场景中锁定分析照片、视频、音频文件等证据复盘分析违法事件。此外，法证建筑还通过数字建模发明了诸多新型工具，对获取和探索创伤记忆进行了新的探索。<br><br>Forensic Architecture (FA), is a research agency founded in 2010, based at Goldsmiths, University of London. They undertake advanced spatial and media investigations into cases of human rights violations, with and on behalf of communities affected by political violence, human rights organizations, international prosecutors, environmental justice groups, and media organizations. Their work often involves open-source investigation, the construction of digital and physical models, 3D animations, virtual reality environments, and cartographic platforms. Within these environments, they locate and analyze photographs, videos, audio files, and testimonies to reconstruct and analyze violent events. They also use their digital models as tools for interviewing survivors of violence, finding new ways to access and explore memories of trauma[imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00046.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00047.jpg\" alt=\"Forensic Architecture - Enter the Void, 2020\r\n美因茨艺术馆\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Forensic Architecture - Enter the Void, 2020<br>美因茨艺术馆</figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00048.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00049.jpg\" alt=\"Forensic Architecture - The Long Duration of a Split Second, 2018\r\n伦敦泰特美术馆 2018年透纳奖提名艺术家展\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Forensic Architecture - The Long Duration of a Split Second, 2018<br>伦敦泰特美术馆 2018年透纳奖提名艺术家展</figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00050.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00051.jpg\" alt=\"Forensic Architecture - Counter Investigations, 2018\r\n伦敦当代艺术中心\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Forensic Architecture - Counter Investigations, 2018<br>伦敦当代艺术中心</figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][sectiondivider]OMA/AMO[sectiontitledivider]大都会建筑事务所 （Office for Metropolitan Architecture），常简称为OMA，为荷兰建筑师雷姆·库哈斯（Rem Koolhaas）于1975年创立。AMO为OMA的分支机构，致力于探索跨学科研究和实践，以生产非建筑项目为主，如艺术展览、品牌设计、出版等。<br><br>Office for Metropolitan Architecture(OMA), is a Dutch architectural firm based in Rotterdam, founded in 1975 by Dutch architect Rem Koolhaas. AMO is a branch of OMA dedicated to producing non-architectural work including exhibitions, branding campaigns, publishin[imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00052.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00053.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00054.jpg\" alt=\"OMA - Countryside: The Future, 2020\r\n纽约古根海姆美术馆\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">OMA - Countryside: The Future, 2020<br>纽约古根海姆美术馆</figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00055.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00056.jpg\" alt=\"OMA - Virgil Abloh: Figures of Speech, 2019\r\n芝加哥当代艺术博物馆\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">OMA - Virgil Abloh: Figures of Speech, 2019<br>芝加哥当代艺术博物馆</figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00057.jpg\" alt=\"OMA - Sun Inlays 2020SS Prada 女装秀场\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">OMA - Sun Inlays 2020SS Prada 女装秀场</figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][sectiondivider]',NULL),(24,1,'2021-02-03 03:43:08','2021-02-03 03:48:42',NULL,'Artist Panel Talk[tagdivider]Diakron ⌁ Tiffany Jaeyeon Shin',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'diakron-tiffany-jaeyeon-shin',NULL,'2020-08-08 19:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary 'Zoom online meeting',_binary '<div class=\"centered\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/r4Ore7v7BnZlwj3z-tmkSA\" target=\"_blank\">活动信息</a></div>[sectiondivider]Diakron[sectiontitledivider]<a>Diakron</a>是一个基于跨学科研究和实践的平台及工作室，以探索性研究为核心价值，在多重学科和体制框架之间建立合作。Diakron的工作模式、实践过程及研究方法不具任何预设性，在保持最大的实验性和开放度的同时，密切关注生态、人道主义、存在主义、数字科技、经济等不同社会层面的发展变化。<br><br>David Hilmer Rex为Diakron的创始人之一，学习于丹麦皇家艺术学院并获得硕士学位，目前在皇家艺术学院职教，并在丹麦奥尔胡斯大学修读博士。<br><br>Diakron is a platform and studio for transdisciplinary research and practice. They are based on explorative research as a core value and establish collaborations across disciplinary backgrounds and institutional frameworks. While their modes of engagement, processes of making, and research methodologies grow out of their projects and collaborations, the work is tied to concerned interests in various pervasive ecological, humanitarian, existential, digital, or economic shifts.<br><br><a>David Hilmer Rex</a>&nbsp;is the co-founder of Diakron. He received MFA at The Royal Danish Academy of Fine Arts, and he is currently teaching at The Royal College of Art, and he is also a PhD student at Aarhus University[imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00058.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00059.jpg\" alt=\"Diakron - Hybrid Organisations \r\nDiakron在2015和2016年拜访了超过40家所谓“混合式组织”，研究不同领域和社区的组织架构、运营模式、思维方法等，最终输出为一份PDF报告。 \"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Diakron - Hybrid Organisations <br>Diakron在2015和2016年拜访了超过40家所谓“混合式组织”，研究不同领域和社区的组织架构、运营模式、思维方法等，最终输出为一份PDF报告。 </figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00060.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00061.jpg\" alt=\"Diakron - Primer\r\n于2016年在丹麦一家开发水净化系统的生物技术公司Aquaporin中成立，通过一系列研究项目、展览等活动，探索新型的组织架构及系统性社会问题间的关系。primer.dk\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Diakron - Primer<br>于2016年在丹麦一家开发水净化系统的生物技术公司Aquaporin中成立，通过一系列研究项目、展览等活动，探索新型的组织架构及系统性社会问题间的关系。primer.dk</figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][sectiondivider]Tiffany Jaeyeon Shin[sectiontitledivider]<a>Tiffany Jaeyeon Shin</a>目前生活并工作于纽约，其艺术作品探索身体边界的渗透性，通过研究活性物质，如食物、气味、微生物、发酵过程等，来思考殖民主义及复杂纠缠的历史关系。<br><br>Tiffany Jaeyeon Shin lives and works in New York. Her work explores the porousness of bodily boundaries and the ceaseless movement of living processes, like fermentation, echoing the history of colonialism. Shin is interested in the history of conquest and the literal digestion of materials – smells, microbes, and food – as a system of relations that emerges from a complicated history of entanglement[imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00062.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00063.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00064.jpg\" alt=\"Tiffany Jaeyeon Shin - Microbial Speculation of Our Gut Feelings, 2019\r\n纽约Recess \"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Tiffany Jaeyeon Shin - Microbial Speculation of Our Gut Feelings, 2019<br>纽约Recess </figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00065.jpg\" alt=\"Tiffany Jaeyeon Shin - Onggi (as if from a firm esophageal column), 2020\r\n纽约DOOSAN画廊\r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Tiffany Jaeyeon Shin - Onggi (as if from a firm esophageal column), 2020<br>纽约DOOSAN画廊<br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00066.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00067.jpg\"></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00068.jpg\" alt=\"Tiffany Jaeyeon Shin - Universal Skin Salvation, 2018\r\n纽约Knockdown中心\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">Tiffany Jaeyeon Shin - Universal Skin Salvation, 2018<br>纽约Knockdown中心</figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][sectiondivider]',NULL),(25,1,'2021-02-03 03:52:14','2021-02-03 03:54:27',NULL,'Critique Marathon[tagdivider]Round Four',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'round-four',NULL,'2020-08-22 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,_binary 'Zoom online meeting',_binary '<div class=\"centered\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/op-FFMW3mJ51-_OOgR8UkQ\" target=\"_blank\">活动信息</a></div>[sectiondivider]08.22[sectiontitledivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00072.jpg\" alt=\"陈沾衣 | 大海回答的问题\r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">陈沾衣 | 大海回答的问题<br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00069.png\" alt=\"滑惜⼦ | 影像连结/Un-exposing\r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">滑惜⼦ | 影像连结/Un-exposing<br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][sectiondivider]08.23[sectiontitledivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00070.jpg\" alt=\"王凯 | \r\n\"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">王凯 | <br></figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][imagedivider]<figure class=\"body-image-holder\"><img src=\"//trigggggggger.local/media/00071.png\" alt=\"杨楠桢 | \"><figcaption class=\"caption caption-roman\">杨楠桢 | </figcaption></figure>[endimagedivider][sectiondivider]',NULL);
